#: _i18n/en/documentation/subscriptions/listening-without-subscribing.md:block
#: 5 (unordered list)
msgid "Don't tap on subscribe but on the episode you want to listen"
msgstr "Натискайте не підписку, а епізод, який хочете прослухати"

#: _i18n/en/documentation/subscriptions/listening-without-subscribing.md:block
#: 5 (unordered list)
